# ğŸ§™â€â™‚ï¸ Agewizard

**Agewizard** is a world-class, magic-like Python library designed to handle all your age and date of birth (DOB) calculations with zero effort. Whether you need an exact age, zodiac signs, or next birthday countdowns, Agewizard does it all in a single line.

[![PyPI Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/agewizard.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/agewizard/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

---

## âœ¨ Features

- **ğŸš€ Instant Age**: Calculate age in years, months, weeks, or days.
- **ï¿½ï¸ Strict Validation**: Automatically catches invalid months (e.g., month 22) or invalid days (e.g., Feb 30).
- **ğŸ“… Customizable Formats**: Supports ANY date format (e.g., `DD-MM-YYYY`, `MM.DD.YYYY`, `YYYY/MM/DD`).
- **ğŸ” Age Verification**: One-line checks for account eligibility (e.g., `is_adult()`).
- **â™ˆ Zodiac Magic**: Get star signs instantly from a DOB.
- **ğŸ‚ Birthday Insights**: Countdown to the next birthday and find out what day of the week it falls on.
- **ğŸ‘¶ Age Classification**: Infant, Child, Teen, Adult, Senior.
- **ğŸŒ— Multi-Cultural**: Basic Hijri lunar age approximation.

